cat_cols = ["UniqueCarrier", "Origin", "Dest", "CancellationCode", "Diverted"]
df[cat_cols] = df[cat_cols].astype("category")

Create a 'FlightDuration' column¶

In [15]:
df["FlightDuration"] = df["CRSElapsedTime"] - df["DepDelay"]

Extract 'Hour' from DepTime¶

In [16]:
df["DepHour"] = df["DepTime"] // 100

Outlier Handling¶

In [17]:
num_cols = ["DepDelay", "ArrDelay", "FlightDuration"]
for col in num_cols:
    q1, q3 = np.percentile(df[col], [25, 75])
    iqr = q3 - q1
    lower_bound, upper_bound = q1 - 1.5 * iqr, q3 + 1.5 * iqr
    df[col] = np.clip(df[col], lower_bound, upper_bound)
